item.title: My First Blog
item.description: The Power of R and Python Semester Update Honestly, I was nervous about taking a computational biology. The idea of making a website made me even more nervous. I would definitely consider myself a novice. However, I enjoyed Biostats, and I was interested in taking another coding course. Seeing that the course fit my degree plan, I registered. Now, it is December! Wow! Another semester complete! My journey in SDS348 was not smooth sailing.
